snippet.title: 【Zgirls】Trailer-English
snippet.description:
Welcom to Zgirls-The world's 1st anime strategy game!
Here, you have to collect and train valkyries with different talents to be your zombie hunters. A huge wave of zombies is coming, are you ready?

【Play for fun】
Google play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.xingjoys.zgirls.gp
App store: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1174204073
